body:
Poi curse has finally broken

after person of interest, I really couldn’t watch any other TV series because - to me -they were like nothing compared to poi.

recently, I was able to force myself into new shows :

1. The good doctor

2. The purge

3. Killing Eve : I’m enjoying it soooo much

They are beautiful, yes, but well poi still on the top.

title: KILLING EVE - S1 Ep 3 & 4
body:
Still bivouacked on my couch using words like bivouacked and drinking liters of hippie echinacea tea, distracting myself with KILLING EVE. It’s like Hannibal meets Le Carré meets, like, GLOW. I’M SO INTO IT. SO MANY WEIRD BABES. IN THS ONE I *CRY*

Season 1, Episode 3 - ‘Don’t I Know You?’

Eve describing Villanelle like Dolly Parton describing Jolene…incredible

Bill, hilarious: agrees with me

wow this BDSM “recreational hospital” is a whole Thing I had no idea even existed!

actually! fun fact: chickens just have the one chute for everything

ah Niko backed me up

Bill has a little bebe!

ooohhhhh sNAP. haha nice move, Vill

just sitting there with her coffee and her cat eye sunglasses, hair all looped up on top of her head

wow Villanelle very very deliberately wants to sleep with Eve!!!!! Killing Eve arrives at the homoerotic killer/detective plot — subtext: text, characters: out.

“Now I am going to HIDE and you are going to FIND ME.” aaahahaasdkfjak

the actor who plays Bill has the same dark crinkly eyes as Mark Rylance

“Anything for this old tart!” yay

…the glitter morgue? these two have stories

is there a scene where Villanelle DOESN’T eat something!

puts Eve’s scarf around her neck then picks up her toothpaste going “Aw!” I CAN’T. [edit: misidentified product! still a gr8 moment]

“Listen, that is massively poignant.”

the Chinese attaché is a trip

Bill’s explaining the contract psychology of how control kinks work and everyone’s like “…”

Bill!

she’s - dressing - her!

fucking superb

EVE & BILL ARE SO CUTE

BILL IS VERY UNEXPECTED AND WELCOME QUEER REPRESENTATION!!?

now Bill’s trying to get Eve to admit she’s bi too, this is GREATSAUCE

Bill if you get murdered I’m gonna through a hissy fit! slow down!

nooooo!!!!! a nightmare!!!!

Bill was my good boy :(

Season 1, Episode 4 - ‘Sorry Baby’

I’m real crying?

eventually the investigator always wants to kill their personal murder bête noire with their bare hands

oh do love those big round ballons

SHE DRESSED UP AS KONSTANTIN FAKE BEARD AND EVERYTHING AND IS SHOUTING HAPPY BIRTHDAY OH MY GOD THAT’S THE MOST FANTASTICALLY WEIRD WAY TO CELEBRATE SOMEONE

my internal monologue just like “cute toy oH MY GOD FEAR”

is it just me or does this fellow assassin have a passing resemblance to Niko

…Anna???

I’m thinking no Anna

“I know you care about me, we all know you care about me. Sometimes I think that’s all you have.” W ow. Eve..

haha Vill’s gonna kill both of them before she kills Eve

she said she hated all her clothes and now HER TERRIBLE MURDER GF BOUGHT HER NEW ONES

SHRIEKING!!!!! SHRIEKING

it delights me on some deep level that Eve is American, like watching Sandra Oh run around London with all these British special agents is tapping into some sort of self-insert fantasy I’ve harbored for years

Eve: [hurries up breathless]
Carolyn, calm, comfortingly stern: “Take a minute.”
Eve: [inarticulate panting]
Carolyn: “Look at the sausages.”
#mom

wow I love Carolyn

“It is disappointing when the mole is the one who looks most like a rodent.” CAROLYN

is this Hot Fuzz

[nearly spills chicken paprikash] aahh the assassins are the ones who just drove into town! they’re here to kill Frank!! shit everything is coming up Frank… and not in a good way for him

yeah, this “team” is just….not as elegant or efficient as Villanelle on her own

Oksana!

nice

oh she’s gonna murderize her, that girl is going under the wheels

bye bye Nadia

dang this is gettin to be all kinds of Le Carré! Russia! moles! how deep does it go! I’m living

Eve: “Frank! Are you running or are you crying?”
Frank: “Running and crying!”
Big Mood

T B C

[ Previously ]
